From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: AutoMint Security <security@automint.app>
Date: Mon, 22 Jun 2026 12:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix(security): close C-1 — remove PRIVATE_KEY fallback

Remove process.env.PRIVATE_KEY from all transaction signing paths.

Changes:
- src/lib/blockchain/mint.ts
  * Add `import 'server-only'`
  * Make userId and walletId required params (was optional)
  * Add runtime guards for empty/whitespace values
  * Replace catch (error) with catch (keyError) + captureException
  * Sanitise returned errors: no walletId, no crypto internals
  * Delete the entire `else { process.env.PRIVATE_KEY }` fallback branch

- src/lib/services/mint-fast.service.ts
  * Add `import 'server-only'`
  * Add captureException on key-decryption errors
  * Sanitise returned errors

- src/lib/blockchain/__tests__/mint.security.test.ts (new)
  * 25 test cases covering all 11 required C-1 scenarios

